Open Design Alliance is a nonprofit organization creating SDKs for engineering applications. ODA offers interoperability tools for .dwg, .dxf, .dgn, Autodesk Revit, Autodesk Navisworks, Autodesk ReCap and .ifc files and a technology stack for visualization, web development, 3D PDF publishing, modeling, and more.  ...mehr

Learn how to run C/C++ code directly in your browser using WebAssembly and Emscripten. This tutorial demonstrates the tools and techniques, including installation and compilation steps. Explore various methods for loading and integrating WebAssembly modules into web applications.
